parameters:
Welcome. If you're looking for lodging on Ancient King's Avenue, please come
to our place.

(As expected, it seems better to return to the church than to stay
here.)

……Ah, umm... It's hard to know where to look, so could you at least
cover it up...

……Are you in the night business? Um, when using our place, please don't
use it for those kinds of things too much.
That's a strange outfit... Or rather, it looks like a swimsuit...
Oh, a customer? If you could please wear something a little more...

Lodging... isn't what you're looking for, right? You're a child of the
church after all.

This is a very old inn that has been around since the time Megista was
built. Well, it has been renovated many times and the original form is
no longer there though.

It's inconvenient for a former capital city to have such poor
transportation... On top of that, there are fewer carriages due to the
monsters, and we have to walk from Marusta...
